message.body: Hey Jim, sorry I missed your call. If you're still around, I'd like to see the upstairs apartment. I'll be available the rest of the day, so we can do this whenever it's convenient for you.
Hey Jim, would you happen to be around today to discuss about the apartment?
Sure. I am not in area but we can talk by phone.
Okay. When would be good for you?
10 minutes I will call you if that works.
Sure. I'll be waiting for your call.
